				<wikidot:authorName>ShadowSpirit90</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6753095</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Spoilers?</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;I'm&nbsp;so&nbsp;lost...</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>I want to give this a +1, but I just feel kinda… Lost. I get that, whatever this&#8230; infection is, it is making them&#8230; count in French, that much is obvious based on the reading and a simple search, but it starts at 5, then 6, then goes to 2, 3, 4. Like, it is a good mystery, and a strange and silly virus, but I feel like I'm just missing something. I want to like it, I really do, but I feel like something is just going over my head.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
